(14666, 'Avazir 0.3% eye oint. 5 gm', 'افازير 0.3% مرهم للعين 5 جم', '18', '26', 'Tobramycin', 'Orchidia pharmaceutical industries', 'Oint', 'مرهم', '', 'Aminoglycoside antibiotic', '0.3%', 'Inhaled tobramycin is indicated for the management of cystic fibrosis patients with _Pseudomonas aeruginosa_, but is not recommended in patients under six years of age, those with forced expiratory volume in 1 second (FEV<sub>1</sub>) <25 or >80% predicted, or in those with _Burkholderia cepacia_.[L32739,L45364]
